Psalm 54

3 O Gód, sáve me by your náme;
by your pówer, defénd my cáuse.
4 O Gód, héar my práyer;
give éar to the wórds of my móuth.

5 For the próud have rísen agáinst me,
and the rúthless séek my lífe.
They have nó regárd for Gód.

6 Sée, I have Gód for my hélp.
The Lórd sustáins my sóul.
7 Let évil recóil on my fóes.
In your fáithfulness, bríng them to an énd.

8 I will sácrifice to yóu with willing héart,
and práise your náme, for it is góod:
9 for it has réscued me from áll distréss,
and my éyes have gázed upon my fóes.
